Package: qmem
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Linux system monitor daemon
 QMem is a modular system monitoring daemon that tracks memory,
 CPU, network, process, and socket statistics. Features include:
 .
  * 10 monitoring services (meminfo, cpuload, netstat, etc.)
  * Dynamic plugin system with hot-reload
  * REST API and web dashboard
  * CLI tool (qmemctl)
  * Unix socket IPC

Package: qmem-plugins
Architecture: any
Depends: qmem (= ${binary:Version}), ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: QMem monitoring plugins
 Dynamic plugin (.so) files for QMem daemon.
 Install to enable loading services as plugins with hot-reload support.
